<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 14:08:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>10 月 7 日，以色列人确信占领是不可避免的。事实恰恰相反</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/october-7-convinced-israelis-the-occupation-is-inevitable-the-opposite-is-true/0000018f-80da-d430-a38f-c5fe949a0000</link><description>与伊朗不同，西岸“哈马斯坦国”的风险不会威胁以色列的存在，也不会威胁以色列民主和全球支持的丧失</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 13:54:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/october-7-convinced-israelis-the-occupation-is-inevitable-the-opposite-is-true/0000018f-80da-d430-a38f-c5fe949a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列卡车开始从西岸向加沙运送人道主义援助物资</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-trucks-begin-transport-of-humanitarian-aid-into-gaza-from-the-west-bank/0000018f-8153-d430-a38f-c5f713960000</link><description>从约旦河西岸开往加沙的卡车数量有所增加，因为警方在国际法院就以色列在拉法的行动举行听证会之前开始采取措施，防止极右翼抗议者封锁和抢劫卡车</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 12:56:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-trucks-begin-transport-of-humanitarian-aid-into-gaza-from-the-west-bank/0000018f-8153-d430-a38f-c5f713960000</guid></item><item><title>随着新疾病和感染的蔓延，加沙的健康危机加剧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/health-crisis-in-gaza-spirals-as-new-diseases-infections-spread/0000018f-7d06-d7f9-a5ff-fd762e1e0000</link><description>数十万巴勒斯坦人遭受急性呼吸道感染和腹泻等问题，不干净的水和不卫生的条件加剧了人道主义局势的恶化。医疗非政府组织警告说，以色列对南部城市拉法的入侵使他们无法提供帮助</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 10:15:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/health-crisis-in-gaza-spirals-as-new-diseases-infections-spread/0000018f-7d06-d7f9-a5ff-fd762e1e0000</guid></item><item><title>五名以色列士兵在加沙北部被以色列国防军坦克炮火打死；三人重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/five-israeli-soldiers-killed-by-idf-tank-fire-in-northern-gaza-three-severely-wounded/0000018f-80a9-d7f9-a5ff-b5ffa8900000</link><description>初步调查显示，位于数十米外的以色列国防军坦克发现了武器，并向加沙北部贾巴利亚难民营的以色列国防军部队发射了炮弹</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 09:58:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/five-israeli-soldiers-killed-by-idf-tank-fire-in-northern-gaza-three-severely-wounded/0000018f-80a9-d7f9-a5ff-b5ffa8900000</guid></item><item><title>约旦河西岸以色列定居者袭击并打伤巴勒斯坦卡车司机，误以为他正在运送加沙援助物资</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settlers-wound-palestinian-truck-driver-falsely-assuming-he-was-hauling-gaza-aid/0000018f-8061-d7f9-a5ff-b577b8600000</link><description>极右翼活动分子在约旦河西岸拦截了多辆卡车，卸下货物，给轮胎放气并纵火焚烧。以色列警方抵达现场并没有逮捕任何嫌疑人</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 08:43:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settlers-wound-palestinian-truck-driver-falsely-assuming-he-was-hauling-gaza-aid/0000018f-8061-d7f9-a5ff-b577b8600000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列拘留期间死亡的加沙医生家人要求调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/family-of-gazan-doctor-who-died-in-israeli-custody-demand-judge-led-investigation/0000018f-803a-d9d6-a38f-85fbfef20001</link><description>Adnan Al-Bursh 医生现年 53 岁，是六个孩子的父亲，也是加沙市 Al-Shifa 医院骨科主任。他的妻子亚斯明 (Yasmin) 与以色列人权医生组织 (PHR) 的代表一起提交了请求</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 08:29:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/family-of-gazan-doctor-who-died-in-israeli-custody-demand-judge-led-investigation/0000018f-803a-d9d6-a38f-85fbfef20001</guid></item><item><title>国际法院就拉法军事入侵举行为期两天的听证会；以色列将于周五提出案件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/icj-opens-two-day-hearings-on-israels-military-incursion-into-rafah/0000018f-803f-d7f9-a5ff-b57f86dc0000</link><description>法律消息人士告诉《国土报》，以色列将辩称，在拉法的行动是针对哈马斯袭击和扣押人质的自卫行动的延续。以色列还将声称正在将巴勒斯坦平民转移到安全地点并向他们提供人道主义援助</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 07:27:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/icj-opens-two-day-hearings-on-israels-military-incursion-into-rafah/0000018f-803f-d7f9-a5ff-b57f86dc0000</guid></item><item><title>军方表示，美国将浮动码​​头停泊在加沙海滩，援助物资将在几天内送达</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/u-s-anchors-floating-pier-to-gaza-beach-aid-to-be-delivered-in-days-centcom-says/0000018f-8011-d430-a38f-c5f5d5aa0000</link><description>拜登于三月份宣布了该码头的建设，当时援助官员恳求以色列改善通过陆路进入加沙的救援物资的通道。美国希望通过开辟海上运送援助的路线来应对导致数十万人面临饥荒风险的人道主义危机</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 06:32:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/u-s-anchors-floating-pier-to-gaza-beach-aid-to-be-delivered-in-days-centcom-says/0000018f-8011-d430-a38f-c5f5d5aa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列研究人员称，神秘的迦南石板原来是学校练习</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-05-16/ty-article/enigmatic-canaanite-tablet-turns-out-to-be-school-exercise-israeli-researchers-say/0000018f-7b85-df8f-a78f-ffdd85dd0000</link><description>近一个世纪前在贝丝谢梅什发现的铭文是由一位崭露头角的抄写员抄写的一系列字母，揭示了近 3,500 年前那里有一所学校的存在</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 06:03:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-05-16/ty-article/enigmatic-canaanite-tablet-turns-out-to-be-school-exercise-israeli-researchers-say/0000018f-7b85-df8f-a78f-ffdd85dd0000</guid></item><item><title>国防部长对内塔尼亚胡的可怕警告暴露了以色列领导层内部的深刻裂痕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/defense-chiefs-warning-to-netanyahu-highlights-the-growing-rift-in-israels-leadership/0000018f-7ddb-d604-af8f-7fdbf5fc0000</link><description>加兰特关于加沙“事后”的声明与甘茨和艾森科特震耳欲聋的沉默形成了鲜明对比——他们两人早就应该表态了。内塔尼亚胡像往常一样决定不做决定。这种公开的裂痕可能会增强哈马斯的信心，并使人质交易更加难以达成</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 03:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/defense-chiefs-warning-to-netanyahu-highlights-the-growing-rift-in-israels-leadership/0000018f-7ddb-d604-af8f-7fdbf5fc0000</guid></item><item><title>南非要求国际法院对以色列“继续屠杀巴勒斯坦人”采取额外措施</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article-live/u-s-backs-israeli-defense-chiefs-call-for-netanyahu-to-reject-military-rule-in-gaza/0000018f-7f05-dd4f-ab8f-ffad91770000</link><description>五名以色列士兵在加沙地带北部被以色列国防军坦克开火打死 ■ 美国军方称加沙岸码头已完工，人道主义援助预计将在未来几天内进入 ■ 以色列士兵在约旦河西岸刺伤事件中中度受伤后，以色列国防军正在调查疑似袭击事件 ■ 真主党声称发射了 60 发子弹以色列北部发射火箭弹，以回应以色列对黎巴嫩的袭击</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 01:39:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article-live/u-s-backs-israeli-defense-chiefs-call-for-netanyahu-to-reject-military-rule-in-gaza/0000018f-7f05-dd4f-ab8f-ffad91770000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长向狡猾的欺诈者内塔尼亚胡发出的信息：你应该受到指责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-chiefs-message-to-netanyahu-the-artful-fraudster-youre-to-blame/0000018f-7e1f-d604-af8f-7f1f0f480000</link><description>为了确保政府能够生存到11月，这位总理再次取消了“征兵法”策略。无奈之下，国防部长约阿夫·加兰特让公众一睹最敏感的战略讨论，并向内塔尼亚胡明确表示：你最好清醒过来——而且要快</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 21:37:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-chiefs-message-to-netanyahu-the-artful-fraudster-youre-to-blame/0000018f-7e1f-d604-af8f-7f1f0f480000</guid></item><item><title>以色列通胀卷土重来，四月份物价涨幅超出预期</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/inflation-is-back-as-april-prices-rise-more-than-expected/0000018f-7dcb-d430-a38f-fdefaf830000</link><description>房价一个月上涨0.95%，特拉维夫上涨2.2% ■ 以色列央行担心新一轮通胀爆发，主要是以色列地缘政治不确定性</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 20:20:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/inflation-is-back-as-april-prices-rise-more-than-expected/0000018f-7dcb-d430-a38f-fdefaf830000</guid></item><item><title>进军加沙还是火炬援助？以色列极右翼如何庆祝独立日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-15/ty-article/.highlight/march-to-gaza-or-torch-aid-how-israels-far-right-celebrated-independence-day/0000018f-7d60-d7f9-a5ff-fd7604220000</link><description>一些以色列人通过焚烧为加沙巴勒斯坦平民提供的援助来标志着以色列的独立。我们彼此的愿望，明年我们享受一个更快乐的假期，似乎越来越远了</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 19:58:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-15/ty-article/.highlight/march-to-gaza-or-torch-aid-how-israels-far-right-celebrated-independence-day/0000018f-7d60-d7f9-a5ff-fd7604220000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡提交甘茨的正统法案草案；甘茨说法律无关紧要</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-submit-gantzs-haredi-draft-bill-gantz-says-law-is-irrelevant/0000018f-7d90-d9d6-a38f-7dfb49530000</link><description>即使以色列总理没有计划真正通过这项法律，他也可以通过阻止高等法院并防止其政府垮台来赢得急需的时间。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 19:38:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-submit-gantzs-haredi-draft-bill-gantz-says-law-is-irrelevant/0000018f-7d90-d9d6-a38f-7dfb49530000</guid></item><item><title>第一所美国大学校长宣布全面抵制以色列学术并休假</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/in-first-california-university-announces-complete-academic-boycott-of-israel/0000018f-7d38-d604-af8f-7f39cc820000</link><description>索诺玛州立大学是一所隶属于加州州立大学系统的公立文理学院，宣布不会与以色列大学建立任何伙伴关系或合作</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 18:09:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/in-first-california-university-announces-complete-academic-boycott-of-israel/0000018f-7d38-d604-af8f-7f39cc820000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长呼吁内塔尼亚胡拒绝对加沙的军事统治</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-minister-calls-on-netanyahu-to-reject-military-rule-in-gaza/0000018f-7ced-d0aa-abbf-feeff9070000</link><description>国防部长加兰特在向内塔尼亚胡发起挑战时表示，“只有取代哈马斯的行动者才能实现哈马斯的未来”。部长们呼吁解雇他</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 17:23:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-minister-calls-on-netanyahu-to-reject-military-rule-in-gaza/0000018f-7ced-d0aa-abbf-feeff9070000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 222 天：Gallant 命令以色列国防军准备关闭约旦河西岸的半岛电视台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-222-gallant-orders-idf-to-prepare-to-shut-down-al-jazeera-in-west-bank/0000018f-7cf9-d0aa-abbf-fefb842d0001</link><description>以色列国防部长呼吁总理内塔尼亚胡公开宣布以色列不会对加沙建立军事统治 ■ 以色列官员警告埃及可能因以色列在拉法的行动而退出停战调解努力 ■ 红十字会在加沙建立野战医院 ■ 超过 60 人以色列北部遭到火箭弹袭击。真主党声称对此次发射负责 ■ 战争进入 222 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 16:11:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-222-gallant-orders-idf-to-prepare-to-shut-down-al-jazeera-in-west-bank/0000018f-7cf9-d0aa-abbf-fefb842d0001</guid></item><item><title>以色列讽刺节目再次攻击亲巴勒斯坦的美国大学生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-satire-show-takes-another-jab-at-pro-palestinian-u-s-college-students/0000018f-7c5f-d604-af8f-7f5f448d0000</link><description>“Eretz Nehederet”草图强调了对抗议参与者的一些最常见的批评——即他们对冲突缺乏真正的理解，以及一些人认为整个运动特征的自恋和特权</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 15:39:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-satire-show-takes-another-jab-at-pro-palestinian-u-s-college-students/0000018f-7c5f-d604-af8f-7f5f448d0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争日记：以色列士兵写下恐惧、痛苦和朋友的死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-gaza-diaries-israeli-soldiers-write-about-fear-agony-and-the-death-of-their-friends/0000018f-72f4-db28-ab8f-f3f5a77f0000</link><description>战斗与反思：自以色列与哈马斯战争爆发以来，许多以色列士兵一直在写个人日记。以下是其中五篇文章的摘录</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 15:01:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-gaza-diaries-israeli-soldiers-write-about-fear-agony-and-the-death-of-their-friends/0000018f-72f4-db28-ab8f-f3f5a77f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>